uk/voices/comment/when--not-if---china-overtakes-the-us-normality-will-have-returned-8644013.html|publisher=[[The_Independent|The Independent]]|accessdate=19 June 2014|archive-date=2015-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926002106/http://www.independent.co.uk/voices/comment/when--not-if---china-overtakes-the-us-normality-will-have-returned-8644013.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>和[[经济史|经济史]]學家[[安格斯·麦迪森|安格斯·麦迪森]]（Angus Maddison）在他所著的《世界經濟千年史》中所說，從[[公元|公元]][[1千紀|一至一千年]]印度曾經構成了的世界最大經濟體。<ref name="Maddisson World GDP">{{cite web|title=The World Economy (GDP) : Historical Statistics by Professor Angus Maddison|url=http://www.theworldeconomy.org/MaddisonTables/MaddisontableB-18.pdf|publisher=World Economy|accessdate=21 May 2013|archive-date=2013-07-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130722202625/http://www.theworldeconomy.org/MaddisonTables/MaddisontableB-18.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Maddison|first=Angus|title=The World Economy - Volume 1: A Millennial Perspective and Volume 2: Historical Statistics|year=2006|publisher=OECD Publishing by [[Organisation_for_Economic_Co-operation_and_Development|Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development]]|location=|isbn=9789264022621|pages=656|url=http://www.oecdbookshop.org/oecd/display.asp?K=5L9ZBQKL5RLW&lang=EN&sort=sort_date%2Fd&stem=true&sf1=Title&st1=world+economy&sf3=SubjectCode&sp1=not&st4=E4+or+E5+or+P5&sf4=SubVersionCode&ds=world+economy%3B+All+Subjects%3B+&m=3&dc=26&plang=en|access-date=2015-07-30|archive-date=2014-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141015104311/http://www.oecdbookshop.org/oecd/display.asp?K=5L9ZBQKL5RLW&lang=EN&sort=sort_date%2Fd&stem=true&sf1=Title&st1=world+economy&sf3=SubjectCode&sp1=not&st4=E4+or+E5+or+P5&sf4=SubVersionCode&ds=world+economy%3B+All+Subjects%3B+&m=3&dc=26&plang=en|dead-url=yes}}</ref>此外，當中國佔有世界經濟主導地位時，印度將會是世界第二大經濟體。<ref name="Maddisson World GDP"/>印度的經濟總量在1700年曾經佔有世界的27%（相比歐洲當時佔有23%），但直至1950年只佔有3%。<ref name="madison1">{{cite book|last=Madison|first=Angus|title=The world economy, Volumes 1–2|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=3NKSC0cgNroC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA638|accessdate=23 May 2013|year=2006|publisher=OECD Publishing|isbn=92-64-02261-9|page=638|doi=10.1787/456125276116|archive-date=2016-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161231140956/https://books.google.com/books?id=3NKSC0cgNroC&lpg=PP1&pg=PA638|dead-url=no}}</ref>也因此許多現代經濟史學家指責殖民地統治者令印度的經濟地位下降。<ref>{{cite book|title=Colonial Power, Colonial Texts: India in the Modern British Novel|first=M. Keith|last=Booker|publisher=University of Michigan|year=1997|pages=153–154|isbn=9780472107803}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|title=Statistics for Economics and indian economic development|author1=T.R. Jain|author2=V.K. Ohri|page=15|isbn=9788190986496|publisher=VK publications}}</ref>

在17世紀時，印度和中國的國內生產總值佔有世界的60%至70%。<ref name="World Powers">{{cite web|title=Will China really dominate?|url=http://www.worldfinance.com/columnists/will-china-really-dominate|publisher=World Finance - The Voice of the Market|accessdate=4 September 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140904163118/http://www.worldfinance.com/columnists/will-china-really-dominate|archive-date=2014-09-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Asia Ascent">{{cite web|title=Asia: A Profile of Economy and Finance|url=http://fofm.in/fofm2012/downloads/Ascent_AsianFinance.pdf|publisher=Future Of Financial Markets (FOFM)|accessdate=4 September 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140722132357/http://fofm.in/fofm2012/downloads/Ascent_AsianFinance.pdf|archivedate=2014年7月22日}}</ref>

== 影響因素 ==

雖然印度已經被確定為一個[[潜在超级大国|潜在超级大国]]，<ref>{{cite journal|url=http://www.twq.com/04winter/docs/04winter_perkovich.pdf|title=Is India a Major Power?|last=Perkovich|first=George|journal=The Washington Quarterly|issue=27.1|date=2003|access-date=2007-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080227014858/http://www.twq.com/04winter/docs/04winter_perkovich.pdf|archive-date=2008-02-27|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite paper |author=Dilip Mohite |title=Swords and Ploughshares- India: The Fourth Great Power? |version=Vol. 7, No. 3 |publisher=Arms Control, Disarmament, and International Security (ACDIS) |date=Spring 1993 |url=http://www.acdis.uiuc.edu/Research/S&Ps/1993-Sp/S&P_VII-3/great_power.html |accessdate=2007-12-13 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20060901150133/http://www.acdis.uiuc.edu/Research/S%26Ps/1993-Sp/S%26P_VII-3/great_power.html |archivedate=2006-09-01 }}</ref>也常被稱為南亞地區的「天生」霸主（例如其在南亞地區擁有的壓倒性優勢，包括政治、經濟、軍事、文化和人口數量），<ref>[http://www.hindustantimes.com/News-Feed/Business/India-s-decade-could-pave-way-for-an-Indian-century/Article1-492147.aspx "‘India’s decade could pave way for an Indian century’."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.hindustantimes.com/News-Feed/Business/India-s-decade-could-pave-way-for-an-Indian-century/Article1-492147.aspx |date=20130508030100 }} ''Hindustan Times.''</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.omantribune.com/index.php?page=news&id=61484&heading=India|title=Next century will be India's, says WSJ - Oman Tribune|work=omantribune|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119002835/http://www.omantribune.com/index.php?page=news&id=61484&heading=India|archivedate=2015-01-19|accessdate=2015-07-30}}</ref>但印度國內存在著深層次的矛盾，極大的[[貧富差距|貧富差距]]和[[基礎建設|基礎建設]]的落後等，若果印度不克服這些問題將會大大阻礙其發展。<ref>[http://www.ufrgs.br/nerint/folder/artigos/artigo5.pdf A Índia e a nova ordem mundial] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ufrgs.br/nerint/folder/artigos/artigo5.pdf |date=20180922153755 }} Universidade Federal do Rio Grande do Sul</ref>

